							<h6 class="b-content-section heading-square heading-border"><a href="/sections/sun-interview">The Sun Interview</a></h6>
		

				<h3 class="block-content-title"><a href="/issues/352/hidden-power">Hidden Power</a></h3>
					<p class="block-content-subtitle subtitle">Noam Chomsky On Resurrecting The Revolutionary Spirit Of America</p>
		

							<ul class="block-content-meta list-inline-border tiny"><li>
							By <a class="meta-article-contributors" href="/contributors/john-malkin">John Malkin</a></li></ul>

		

					</div>


		
</article>

											
	

